title: Losing Control: Physiologically, it Looks an Awful Lot Like Fear
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary:
The second episode of our series, Losing Control, features All the Rage co-hosts Ryan and Chuck interviewing cognitive neuroscientist Dr. Jason Cowell. During this episode, they investigate just what happens in our brains when we get mad.

Learn more here: www.alltheragescience.com
